Jeanetta Riley, 35, was killed last July after she brandished a knife at two cops outside of a hospital in Sandpoint on July 8, 2014 .
She was taken to hospital by her husband, Shane, after he heard her fiddling with blades and talking about stabbing people .
Officers Michael Valenzuela, 27, and Skyler Ziegler, 29, were cleared of any wrongdoing following the incident and the case was closed in November .